title: Did you tell Hillary Clinton Muller of the FBI to hand over uranium to the Russians in 2009 'Surt Tarmac meeting'?
subtitle: The extremist party websites misdescribed Kabul as the State Department, which alerted the United States Embassy in Russia to the transfer of criminal evidence obtained in a stinging operation.
author: David Emery
vclaim: Foreign Minister Clinton then ordered the then FBI Director Robert Mueller to hand over HEU to the Russians at a secret meeting on the side of the aircraft in 2009.
